                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for second half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-162ra)&#xD; I-1) Maggābit (fols. 2ra-26vb)&#xD; I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     27ra-45rc)&#xD; I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 45va-71v)&#xD; I-4) Sane (fols.
